title: HSN | The List with Colleen Lopez 10.12.2017 - 10 PM
description:
We're bringing you an entire episode of Colleen Lopez fashions! Plus RJ Graziano stops by to give us some jewelry styling tips. Curator and host Colleen Lopez takes the guesswork out of style by showcasing her weekly favorites.
